1.title: Dead Beach Part 1
1.plot: Karl is lost. Which is somewhat of an understatement. And in his attempt to find help he may just find out he is more lost than he had initially suspected.

2.title: Urban Red
2.plot: Scarlett was expecting to have a pleasant late night picnic with her boyfriend Carter, until her night took turn for the worse and she was rescued by Lupin. Sometimes things go from bad to worse.

3.title: Wil-O-Wisp
3.plot: Sometimes we see ripples of the past, echoes of those long since passed from the world. When Roan comes to the aid of Scarlett, he discovered a side of life he had never seen before.

4.title: Bloodsoaked Past
4.plot: Jenny twisted her ankle and couldn't go dancing with Logan, instead he's invited her to his place for dinner. She finds his vocation as a magicians apprentice alluring, she is curious to find out more. Curiosity is, of course, one of our more dangerous traits.

5.title: Bridge Bunny
5.plot: Roan's encounter with Scarlett's wraith form lead him on a dangerous path to uncover the truth behind the supernatural. He's been hunting down these creatures and 'dealing' with them for months. Now he has a new target, but it seems the Bridge Bunny only appears in the presence of women. Surely, that's not going to stop him.

6.title: Dead Beach Part 2
6.plot: Lucy has been grieving for her missing brother Karl for many months. His body was never found but it is assumed he's dead. Paul her boyfriend has stuck by Lucy, and now, at the most unexpected of times they are pulled into the land of the lost. Why are they in Dead Beach? Will they find their way out before they are consumed by the souls of the lost?

7.title: The Drive Home
7.plot: Abbey is a hard worker, in fact she is often the last to leave work, staying back to finish filling away the freshly typed documents. She lives with her friend and her dog, and like all young women in the area is a little disturbed by the recent string of attacks and deaths. The police advice women to be careful and she's not taking any chances.

imdb.plot outline: The rise in supernatural activity calls into action men and women who would have otherwise lived a normal life. Do they stand and fight; do they turn their backs; or is their fate already decided. Only time will reveal the truth behind the growing dark presence. And who is this mysterious narrator, who knows more than he is letting on.
